%C - shutdown the system (Neutrino)

%C	[options]
Options:
 -S type  Shutdown type. Type: system|reboot (default:reboot).
 -f       Fast shutdown.
 -n node  Node to shutdown. Default is current node.
 -b       Shutdown but do not reboot.  May not be used with -n node.
 -q       Quiet.
 -v       Verbose.
